               <occupation type="ruler">Emperor</occupation>

               <floruit notBefore="1603" notAfter="1604">He became a king in <date>1603</date>.
                  He introduced  a reform to form an organized army under his command and he also made a reform of land ownership to the peasants with a motto “Man is free, land
                  is tributary”. He was a pro-Catholicism and very close to <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7699Paez">Pedro Páez</persName>
               </floruit>
               <death when="1604" evidence="internal">October 1604</death>

